Methods

RegisterSession ( s )

Description: Register a new application session to the manager. This session will now be managed by it until the application releases it session.

Parameters

s: appname

The common name of the application. Should look like "org.foo.bar".

ReleaseSession ( )

Description: Release a session registered before with the manager. FIXME add a note about which signals the session will be received before it gets really released by the manager.
